0.2.0 ()
=====
* Changed send function to 
  use Unix.write instead of Pervasives.
  This has been reported to generate much less load.
* Added manual_update_metadata to 
  update metadata on any source with being
  previously connected/streaming on it.

0.1.1 (2009-10-26)
=====
* Fixed ICY source connection; send 
  headers only after receiving "OK2"
* Fixed error: Scanf may raise other exceptions,
  catching any of them now..
0.1.0 (2009-10-12)
=====
* Initial release
